Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是布拉德·T·麗茲大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.38,0:00:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據記錄 您哥哥應該跟您在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人已經先回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.89,0:00:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們並未接到這樣的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.13,0:00:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我趕時間 快點讓我過去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.01,0:00:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.88,0:00:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝羅斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.99,0:00:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來 我帶你回府邸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.81,0:00:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝羅斯大人 您臉上沾了口香糖…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:10.10,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H7D3785&}兩個人都是財富
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.95,0:02:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你應該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是負責殿堂治安的殿堂警察
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來找你哥哥有事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻被他巧妙地避開了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因…因為有急事 所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不通報一聲就擅自出入 光這一點就夠定罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我也因此才有了可以用特權帶走他的理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要把哥哥大人帶去哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶去他最不想見到的人那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.31,0:02:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶去殿堂魔界王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏爾夫·達迪那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要去那種傢伙那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我注意你的用詞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他找哥哥大人有何貴幹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我可不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:02:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是機密事項
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種傢伙才不是王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他從我們身邊奪走了爸爸和媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.12,0:03:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 聖誕老人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人來了 我離開下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你繼續工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 變態眼鏡 我知道你在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.65,0:03:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不趕快出來的話 你可愛的妹妹會怎麼樣我可不管哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把別人說的好像人質一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你叫他出來啊 話說你把我放進去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是一點都沒變啊貝羅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何貴幹？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要給我裝作不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先閉嘴給我把門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人 不可以打開 這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然直接衝了過來 確定是這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯 色澤香味俱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我在下面找到的香草茶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調製的不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未經手續就進入殿堂是犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要逮捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能保持這麼淡定的樣子也就只有現在了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的特權敗家犬的項圈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不管去到任何地方都會跟隨你的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敗家犬的項圈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著這個項圈的人不允許使用任何魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果使用了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那杯香草茶就會混入你的血了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這種原理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:05:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能被你飼養也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 帶我去散步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我沒有聽哥哥大人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的麗茲 我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不能拖延時間 看家是可以做到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見麗茲 要乖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麗茲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道冬實在哪裏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.93,0:05:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 你又哭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒哭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是哭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人 因為我回來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抓走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不就沒法搜尋冬實了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以搜尋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:06:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在黑漆漆一片 無法觀察到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個外來人在大路中間說個什麼勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人困擾啊 說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗茲 知道什麼的話再聯絡我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你什麼錯也沒有 不要再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒哭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊怎麼 難道說結束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那來跟我聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識這個男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不到啊 喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,額 對不起 我沒見過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫不上您 萬分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 但是老大也許真的認識
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的是個情報通
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 我來帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那就帶路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊 跟我來就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說在前頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是敢騙我的話 下次我絕對會殺了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:06:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞錯了 應該是這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪 我帶客人來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀這個人好像遇上麻煩了我就好心的帶他來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百分之百的出於好心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 這裏凍死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 因為我是雪男所以周圍都很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦好冷好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己都覺得冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們老大很滑稽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你為什麼不覺得冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢？聽鯖夫說你遇上麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫鯖夫 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找這個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥你從哪裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有印象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊對了 火鍋 吃火鍋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷的時候就要吃火鍋吧 真的 湯鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,yeah 吃湯鍋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.36,0:07:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我認識他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不知道他現在在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我大概知道他家在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有名片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這附近嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我覺得你去不了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次元街道 魔界七大不可思議之一的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際也沒有去過或者見過的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說他回到那裏的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法追到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是他還在附近就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼魯君 這是名片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是送快遞的 有不可思議的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的妥協拉麵 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊也該餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 再來一碗拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好勒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我的格子房間感覺如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柳冬實
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的妥協拉麵 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是醃雞蛋絕對不會妥協的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝 這裏沒有任何機關哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行啊 連碗都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的碗絕不妥協 賠我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不付錢我可是不會妥協的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該出手時就出手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把碗還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 放開 燙死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湯濺到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你想跟我搶 我也不會妥協的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬實叫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:09:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼他會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從昨天開始就喝多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麗茲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史塔茲 我知道冬實在哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一個奇怪的男人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}什麼都能運到 海德拉·尼魯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也弄清這個男人的身份了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快點了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個感覺有點不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你會中招呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見呢 尼魯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一點都沒變 我放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是受誰所雇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是知道你運送的物品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬實是我的朋友 你擅自對她下手我會很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.19,0:11:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你發了好幾次郵件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實姐姐才適合幹這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.61,0:11:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是跑腿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為聯繫不上你 媽媽可是很生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 為什麼媽媽要對冬實…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 幽靈小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史塔茲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 那邊也火大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:33.12,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38\c&H0E00C2&}再見 幽靈小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是告訴她被帶回去了 媽媽會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 尼魯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝魯 你也有份嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在剛剛參與進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是敵是友 給我說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敵人的話 我是不會留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是急性子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.45,0:11:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能給我點時間猶豫一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我管你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把冬實還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:12:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼魯 剩下的就交給姐姐 去用那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我向媽媽問好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬實就在那裏面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 拉麵那時承蒙關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.14,0:12:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你待在那裏不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有可以的話 現在開始不要看我要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把腳露出一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白的話 就拿回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是陷阱吧 你拿來給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天老是打不中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打得中才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 逃得掉麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這邊可不會打不中的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要妨礙我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道 這樣下去冬實會消失的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是與我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個鈴鐺不是為了保護冬實才交給她的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是保護她了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥給冬實裝了發信器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他知道會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你阻止我也在大哥的計劃之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我奪回冬實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就那麼重視她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬實是我的唯一限定品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白嗎 她是唯一的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失以後就再也得不到的稀有品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白的吧 賞金獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.75,0:13:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我徹底生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38\c&H65FF80&\3c&H0F230A&}臨界點突破！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是那麼重視她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.51,0:14:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻這樣看待我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決鬥吧 要是你贏了我就帶你去冬實的所在之處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到海德拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我來到了像昨天看過的動畫一樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你好像誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 你這個宅男吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你誤會了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要生氣啊 生氣的人應該是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以叫你過來干一架啊 你這個宅男吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是想踢我的屁股直到我說「我輸了」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是為了這個才取出子彈的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就來試試看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試看能不能追上我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用沒用 你是無法追上我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 後面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經倒下了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你把我的T恤弄得像健次郎一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}北斗神拳的健次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了的話就放棄冬實 一生一世當我的奴隸如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊 我是不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種話等你站起來再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被只露出臉的人說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是蘇打餅幹上的作料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你就沒什麼可抱怨的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.21,0:15:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都跟你說沒用了 你要試幾次才能學乖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經切身體會到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要被關進這裏 你就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點認輸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像之前那樣 說「我輸了」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜 我不是之前的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔力的具體化 你也能做得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊 剛才已經拿出來做了好幾次無用功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我的魔力現在在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太得意忘形了 貝魯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個真討厭 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說「我輸了」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話 就要跟你的下半身說再見了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實是大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還…還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史塔茲先生 好高啊 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.88,0:17:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話我有點快嚇尿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最喜歡的日本漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是在那裏出場的英雄們的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 你想讓我把這個套在頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.77,0:17:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者「嘶哈嘶哈」的聞個不停嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.42,0:17:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊變態
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是哪門子的英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說那種好像拿著髒東西一樣的拿法讓我很受傷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:18:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 我在撿到這個的時候想把它作為交易材料的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「說啊 想讓我把這個還給你的話就說你輸了」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算做這種惡劣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我很快就發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝魯會用看垃圾一樣的眼神看我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後空間移動回房間慢慢換衣服就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會變得像小丑一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:22.49,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\c&H000000&\pos(168,296)}垃\N圾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這麼做真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我放到一邊快點逃走不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說她沒有注意到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說這其實是很厲害的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說貝魯為什麼還在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止沒有逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好像很怕我做什麼似的一臉不安 這表情是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個內褲是寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包裏那本列著我想要的東西的 秘密的寶物手冊裏史塔茲那頁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被發現了我肯定會羞恥到死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 如果只是那樣的話還好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.29,0:19:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那後面還有我喝醉的時候記錄下的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「史塔茲為我神魂顛倒大作戰」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到那個會被看到…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有洞的話 我真想鑽進去住上六天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看到就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是我的感情被發現 還一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}多謝觀看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個放進這裏面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是很重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有很多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不放開沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.32,0:19:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 我總算懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在ONIQLO的時候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡是跟你扯上關係的內褲都是虛晃一槍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真正在意的是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要敢看 我就開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧 開槍毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也學乖點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這邊來 一起看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看 NO.163餐點用配花（已買）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}說 我說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說「我輸了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有必要把我提起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個 我忘了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 現在的我沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會觸犯了什麼播放限製法令之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重裝子彈之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把內褲穿上…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會沒事 失血太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 這都是你幹的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我真搞不懂你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然生氣起來要跟我決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因為被看了日記輕易就認輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.66,0:21:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是因為你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去救你最愛的冬實吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你 誰叫我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那麼拚命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拚命到都看不到周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,0:21:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄冬實就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你也帶不回她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的血明明也不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻只想著要分給她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明在你眼前的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.39,0:21:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算對著你張開雙臂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.38,0:21:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擋住你的視線對你說「看著我」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你卻會無視我 像笨蛋一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能說「我輸了」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不清楚狀況 錯在我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.19,0:21:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:21:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管做什麼 說到底多數錯也在我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.93,0:22:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你會這麼奇怪也是我的錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是 也當成是我的錯就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.42,0:22:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.71,0:22:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結論是我不像英雄 反而更像是壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你有什麼生氣的事就把發洩到我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.33,0:22:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罵我也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說「全都是你的錯」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.72,0:22:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我是不會道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.75,0:22:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 說說看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.37,0:24:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.23,0:24:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊 人家好不容易…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.73,0:24:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了 謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.36,0:24:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧 差點就說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.27,0:24:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜說「我輸了」也要隱藏起來的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.33,0:24:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是你的錯 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.93,0:24:34.94,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs55\c&H000000&\pos(1002,598)\3c&H3AFFFE&}眼鏡的罪過
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.64,0:24:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部長 你快想想辦法啊那個可惡的眼鏡煩死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.17,0:24:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐 貝羅斯巡查
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.51,0:24:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王下令要活著帶他來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.55,0:24:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.73,0:24:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我超想殺他！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.41,0:24:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 BLOOD LAD 眼鏡的罪過
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.51,0:24:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔界只有壞孩子哦
